<item>
            <title>[LU-12871] enable changelog garbage collection by default</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12871</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This feature was disabled by default in commit v2_10_56_0-2-g3442db6fa (2.11.0) and was fixed in commit v2_11_52_0-59-g31fef6845e (2.12), but was not re-enabled again by default.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a very useful functionality as sites often register Changelog users but forget to remove them, causing problems with the MDT running out of space or the Changelog becoming full.  Enable it again by default.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
